casebody.data:
ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND v. FABIAN H. KOLKER [Misc. (BV) No. 30,

September Term, 1982.]

Order filed October 11, 1983.

Consent to disbarment filed by Fabian H. Kolker in accordance with Maryland Rule BV12 d 2.

Fabian H. Kolker is disbarred by consent from the further practice of law in the State of Maryland and his name stricken from the register of attorneys in this Court.
